CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1956, pg. 6 reads: "Hopes For The Future - This is the board of governors of Loendi Club which has the responsibility of planning the course of the club for years to come. Included in the photo are: Robert T. McEnheimer, president; Atty. Paul F. Jones, vice president; Howard Hairston, secretary; Benjamin C. Frazier, corresponding secretary; Stanley McD. Williams, treasurer, and members Roland M. Sawyer, Shedrick Fields, Byron N. Peters, William E. Williams, Walter C. Rainey, John M. Burton, Dr. Clarence C. Blow, Dr. Woodford A. Harris, Walter H. Patterson, William G. Nunn Sr., and Leo McTurner.  Atty. W. Wendell Stanton was out of town at the time the picture was made. - Harris Photo."
